'''Teh''' was a [[H'kig]] glyph that represented a mystical ideal of the peaceful religion. Considered too sacred to be written in full, the glyph was often abbreviation was "t". The glyph translated roughly into "the transcendent."<ref name="Wizards">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20030130jtptan|text=J't'p'tan: Temples and Tybis}}</ref>

